{"tid":1773150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳： OL救星　一年睇1800對腳","createTime":"2019-12-07T08:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T15:08:16.000Z","uid":297241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"57619691269237517a8cd1563b49eda083811de7","tid":1773150,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:58:17.000Z","msg":"隔牆有耳： OL救星　一年睇1800對腳<br />\n<br />\nOL着起高踭鞋婀娜多姿，實際有苦自己知，好多人雙腳被高跟鞋夾到變形，唔怪得駐診中環嘅足病診療師（ Podiatrist）劉庭耀（ Ryan）門庭若巿啦。<br />\n<br />\n全港認可註冊足病診療師僅30多位，做咗10年嘅 Ryan受聘醫療集團，亦有在私家醫院掛單，仲要照顧埋醫管局足病門診嘅病人，每日平均睇30人，一周五天工作，有數得計，一年經佢手診治就有1,800對腳。"},{"pid":"d1dcee9e7af6b06c5d526c06dcd5ed04ac158779","tid":1773150,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:59:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAmC1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAmC1f.jpg&h=565489c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQkE87V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQkE87V.jpg&h=ca6df116&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2a424f59c9808f84bcaba5d3c98638ba35a7e86","tid":1773150,"uid":343268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T09:02:31.000Z","msg":"早知努力啲讀書<img src=